'''''Titus as a Monk''''' or '''''Rembrandt's Son Titus in a Monk's Habit''''' is a 1660 oil on canvas painting by the Dutch artist [[Rembrandt]], showing his son [[Titus van Rijn|Titus]] in the habit of a [[Franciscan]] monk. It is now in the collection of the [[Rijksmuseum]] in [[Amsterdam]].
==External links== * [http://www.rijksmuseum.nl/aria/aria_assets/SK-A-3138?lang=en ''Rembrandt’s Son Titus in a Monk’s Habit'', Rembrandt Harmensz. van Rijn, 1660]
